wool roller
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a member of a shearing gang who skirts and rolls fleeced on the wool-table.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
